title: New Jersey Comic Expo Exhibitor Booths
desc: Exhibitor booths and Artist Alley tables are available on a first come, first serve basis. Please use this site to pay for your space using the secure payment processor. You will need to complete and submit a registration form which is available on  . Please contact Carly at cmarsh@madeventmanagement.com if you have any questions or concerns. Once you have completed your registration and confirmed that it has been received, we will send details about the move-in and booth assignments approximately 2 weeks prior to the event start date.
